Pamela O'DONNELL, Individually, as Administratrix ad Prosequendum for the Estate of Timothy O'Donnell, as Administratrix ad Prosequendum for the Estate of B.O., a Minor, and as Guardian ad Litem of A.O., a Minor, Plaintiffs-Movants,
v.
NEW JERSEY TURNPIKE AUTHORITY, Defendant-Respondent,
and
Service McCabe Ambulance, Elisar Morales and Scott Hahn, Defendants. M-1057/1058 September Term 2017
080735 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 21, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion to expand the record (M-1057) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion to take judicial notice of records (M-1058) is denied.
